survey_response.review_text: The doctor was very friendly, and the way she patiently heard us and answered all of our queries are much appreciated.

Very friendly doctor.... Caring towards the baby was awesome!.The way you explained things would make us understand issue clear, thanks for that!and also.. diet plan you give for my son.!!.The conversation and consultation was just great. #Recommended.

review_reply.reply_text: Thank you for the kind words

survey_response.review_text: She gives proper advice which is very beneficial to ur baby and mother. Dr. Shilpa was the one who used to come for a round when my wife and baby were admitted after delivery. We liked the way she speaks and explains the things which you don’t know to handle it properly. We did not know her name that time but fortunately for my baby review after 3 days we got An appointment with Dr. Shilpa only though I was asked to review with some other doctor. Best part is she is very vocal. I would definitely recommend people to visit her when you need pediatrician...

Dr.shilpa was really good professional to check for kids. my son (lenin) got viral fever and we consultant dr.shilpa, she gave proper explanation about the issue with right treatment. thank you doctor.
Very friendly madam. Explains the health issues very well. A ever smiling face. Responds very well whenever needeed.

She treat my baby not like a doctor but a mother 🤱🏻
She is so soft hearted doctor and she understand what baby need , care and love
